The Kvika Reykjavik Open is a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 6–12 April 2022 in Reykjavik, Iceland.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.reykjavikopen.com
